No. 09-1150. Universal Trading & Investment Company, Inc., Petitioner v. Petro Mikolayevich Kiritchenko, et al. 561 U.S. 1038, 130 S. Ct. 3504,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1114,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5308. June 28, 2010.

Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of the petition for writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 346 Fed. Appx. 232.
